y to unlock the many different ping pong balls this game has to offer. Bring the party to your headset with Beer Pong Basement!", "short_description": "Play the classic party game of beer pong in virtual reality! Invite a friend to play or challenge a training robot. Choose regular beer pong or spice things up with power-ups. Take a break and watch YouTube videos, or try your luck at the slot machine or arcade game to earn credits. Try to unlock the many different ping pong balls as you play. Get ready to bring the party to your headset with Beer Pong Basement!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://jonasbellmann.wixsite.com/beerpongbasement/terms", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Jonas Bellmann", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sidequestvr.com/app/5185/beer-pong-basement", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1700921480735423"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["CASUAL", "SOCIAL"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "SINGLE_USER"], "id": "492920262759560"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1129246181089397"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1022935012471827"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1022935012471827"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1674255600, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1129246181089397"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test